{"tid":441573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《血洗洪花亭》係咪本地史上最誇張劈友電影","createTime":"2017-10-19T18:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T09:58:25.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5cffa03c800f54d566bd21a65cc8648eb48825d7","tid":441573,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T18:58:01.000Z","msg":"有日搵下舊片無意中睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?&amp;v=5zpyAohQunA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3F%26v%3D5zpyAohQunA&d=q3BFxFtv%2FWsKmbnTaQQ%2FX7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=44d6a59c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?&amp;v=5zpyAohQunA</a>"},{"pid":"1ffa6fe60948267f9f6c9d8afba12d013ca5c7c1","tid":441573,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T18:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/血洗洪花亭\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E8%A1%80%E6%B4%97%E6%B4%AA%E8%8A%B1%E4%BA%AD&d=q3BFxFtv%2FWsKmbnTaQQ%2FX7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=65a84815\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/血洗洪花亭</a><br />\n<br />\n此戲來自1990年由柯星沛導演；王祖賢、莫少聰、林俊賢、龍方等主演<br />\n<br />\n此片描黑幫頭目之女阿鳳接掌堂口，欲取締其父之非法生意，卻被其部下窮追猛打。阿鳳與任職警官的男友身分懸殊（參照<ins>香港警察與三合會關係</ins>），暗戀阿鳳的警長也參與混戰，惟功敗垂成。正當堂口內鬨白熱化之時，阿鳳施計粉碎了一宗軍火買賣，藉以消除其夫的黑勢力。<br />\n<br />\n根據《<ins>電影檢查條例</ins>》，本片因有正面描寫連環斬人等的過度暴力，雖然江湖儀式、阿勇自首等鏡頭被刪剪（台灣版錄影帶仍然保留），但仍被評定為<ins>第三級影片</ins>。"},{"pid":"b9a2125d820039868a382958775217a704365cce","tid":441573,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T19:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=oqPSMO9PoK4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoqPSMO9PoK4&d=q3BFxFtv%2FWsKmbnTaQQ%2FX7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=89fa4d1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=oqPSMO9PoK4</a><br />\n全套<img src=\"